inside this div luck,

00:02:13.790 --> 00:02:15.470
although a def block takes up

00:02:15.470 --> 00:02:18.229
the whole width of the
canvas by default,

00:02:18.229 --> 00:02:21.800
we can also give it a
specific width and height.

00:02:21.800 --> 00:02:24.110
If you head over to
the Size section

00:02:24.110 --> 00:02:25.805
on the style panel here,

00:02:25.805 --> 00:02:28.940
you can specify a
particular width, e.g.

00:02:28.940 --> 00:02:30.770
400 pixels.

00:02:30.770 --> 00:02:31.745
And there we go.

00:02:31.745 --> 00:02:33.680
We can modify the
height as well.

00:02:33.680 --> 00:02:36.365
You can set it to 300 pixels

00:02:36.365 --> 00:02:39.785
